snippet.title: Projekt Z: Beyond Order - Indie Horror Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Projekt Z: Beyond Order will be available on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series and PC next Spring 2025.

Today’s announcement is featuring new footage of the zombies you’ll be slaying and the weapons you’ll be doing it with! Welcome to the Overview Trailer for the Indie Horror Showcase 2024! 

Visit: https://www.projektzgame.com
Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/763310/Projekt_Z_Beyond_Order/

Follow Us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/maximumentmt
Watch us on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@maximumentmt
Like Us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MaximumEnt/
Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/maxent
